      "totalCount": 962,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=552&rangeEnd=597",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=552&rangeEnd=597"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_3831-3911",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3831-3911",
      "markText": "是岁，巴延请杀张、王、刘、李、赵五姓汉人，帝不从。是为宰相起意屠戮汉人，先就人数最多之姓为始。以姓分应杀不应杀，设想已极不道，帝虽不从，此风声已不可令天下闻矣。",
      "totalCount": 357,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3831&rangeEnd=3911",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3831&rangeEnd=3911"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_6_1047-1116",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1047-1116",
      "markText": "宦官无代不能为患，而以明代为极甚。历代宦官与士大夫为对立，士大夫决不与宦官为缘。明代则士大夫之大有作为者，亦往往有宦官为之助而始有以自见。",
      "totalCount": 338,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1047&rangeEnd=1116",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1047&rangeEnd=1116"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_12798-12823",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12798-12823",
      "markText": "国之兴亡系于财之丰耗，阜财者，民也；耗财者，军也。",
      "totalCount": 320,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12798&rangeEnd=12823",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12798&rangeEnd=12823"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_2658-2721",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2658-2721",
      "markText": "元亦并无经久之兵制，一往用其饥穷为暴、胁众觅食之故技，侵掠万里，既得温饱，即伎俩无复存焉，非若历代军制既定，威令久而后渝者比。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2658&rangeEnd=2721",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2658&rangeEnd=2721"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_9_31810-31890",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "31810-31890",
      "markText": "一日，帝往西内，熟视高煦锁絷状，高煦出不意伸一足勾上踣地，上大怒，命力士舁三百斤铜缸覆之，煦多力，顶负缸起，积炭缸上如山，燃炭逾时，火炽铜锫，高煦死，诸子皆死。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=31810&rangeEnd=31890",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=31810&rangeEnd=31890"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_1617-1687",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1617-1687",
      "markText": "所谓“马上得之，马上治之”。不知礼法刑政为何事。凡历朝享国稍久者，必有一朝之制度。制度渐坏，国祚渐衰。有经久难坏之制度，即有历久始衰之国祚。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1617&rangeEnd=1687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1617&rangeEnd=1687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_19486-19579",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "19486-19579",
      "markText": "洪武十五年五月丙子，广平府吏王允道言：“磁州产铁，元时置官，岁收百余万斤，请如旧。”帝曰：“朕闻王者使天下无遗贤，不闻无遗利。今军器不乏，而民业已定，无益于国，且重扰民。”杖之，流岭南。",
      "totalCount": 256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=19486&rangeEnd=19579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=19486&rangeEnd=19579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_6749-6774",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6749-6774",
      "markText": "三代以下，名为禅让，实乃篡夺，得国唯以革命为正大。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6749&rangeEnd=6774",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6749&rangeEnd=6774"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_813-833",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "813-833",
      "markText": "清无制作，尽守明之制作，而国祚亦与明相等",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=814402&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=813&rangeEnd=833",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e9e320905c6d42e9e7809b2?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=813&rangeEnd=833"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "814402_8_15723-15810",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "15723-15810",
